title: Editor Messages
tags: [[Card Features]]

The card edit template displays the same editor messages as does the main edit template, and one new message from Dropboard.

The checkbox "Update tags and list fields" is displayed when the title has changed.
<br>
The warning "Avoid using characters `| [ ] { }` in title" is displayed when those characters are found in the "title" field.

[[The new warning|Warning: No Multiline Shorttext]] "Avoid multiple lines in shorttext" is displayed when newline characters ( `\n` ) are found in the "shorttext" field.